{"tid":34824,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"失婚男 你問我答","createTime":"2016-12-11T16:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T16:50:36.000Z","uid":60800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae0c84c78a1be0a9939aeb66216a0c21aa3fc596","tid":34824,"uid":60800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:36:02.000Z","msg":"係失婚 婚姻失敗<br />\n老婆有婚外情要走 <br />\n始終早婚 要怪只可以怪自己做得未夠<br />\n小妹妹始終未識得珍惜安定<br />\n<br />\n坐係自己架車到不斷喊<br />\n一邊聽國腎嘅 我們都不是無辜的<br />\n一邊上高速狂飛再鳩喊鳩嗌<br />\n<br />\n只係上星期嘅事 律師都未搵得切唔好話放低<br />\n係唔係酒醒又一條好漢真係唔知<br />\n<br />\n知道嘅係<br />\n<br />\n我依一世都會揹起婚姻失敗依四個字行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">求巴打們屌醒 我連翻入房面對嘅勇氣都無 坐係後園煲左好耐煙<strong><del><del></del></del></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2de3161872d334dbbfdc141a96f9eb333c9c2918","tid":34824,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:40:00.000Z","msg":"老婆去左邊？係房？BTW RIP"},{"pid":"e856928226b71093a330cf9605196705a4f01c2d","tid":34824,"uid":38405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:42:27.000Z","msg":"相差幾年？"},{"pid":"d5283c6f26aa8e63224761ecca25fa35a2ded4be","tid":34824,"uid":60800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老婆去左邊？係房？BTW RIP</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係房 依家等佢訓我先翻去 係出面5，6個鐘戇鳩鳩"},{"pid":"18510c181a10811bab87aa4981084c6cabdb2494","tid":34824,"uid":60800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相差幾年？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2年 我捱緊世界果時識佢 年幾就結婚 結婚半年就到左依一刻"},{"pid":"22ed36e20cdace599ae761955ad0a4226172e742","tid":34824,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:50:36.000Z","msg":"姦夫咩人黎 你識唔識<br />\n點樣發現<br />\n有無去打鳩佢"}]}